title: Tea Shrine
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Chinese, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out
description: Offers inexpensive quick meals that are filling. Most have a mock meat component plus sauce, rice, and a side of salad. There are also sandwiches, steamed buns, and stir fried entrees. Large variety of teas, served hot or iced. Some mock meats contain milk products (so ask. Some meals include egg components, like rice with fried egg. Some diary desserts. Honey in some fresh juice combos.
